{"tid":2066510,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"新手想出車，第三保問題","createTime":"2020-06-16T10:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T07:16:19.000Z","uid":57186,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"12cc9047ee8dd8d370c8b0298478ec531d9da571","tid":2066510,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:33:39.000Z","msg":"想問下，p牌仔同甩p無耐去買三保個價錢會唔會差好遠？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上網睇就無講清楚，只係話25歲前後好大分別，同埋駕駛經驗越多就越平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有fd話p同岩岩甩無咩分別，係有甩p再多1年(計埋p total 2年牌)先開始有分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打解答下，如果其實都有分別，想知兩者個實際保費大約差幾多%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e23e17251d12e166d0796a233ec7af756ca24c","tid":2066510,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"未夠25啱啱甩P 三保都係4k有找"},{"pid":"bf107da9a9bec88de29fa24d9fc10218a4ce427f","tid":2066510,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"但係如果未甩，冇6k你唔洗落樓"},{"pid":"57afebd4ef9aea474ba58d611ddd59e17d734a0b","tid":2066510,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf107da9a9bec88de29fa24d9fc10218a4ce427f","tid":2066510,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:37:45.000Z","msg":"但係如果未甩，冇6k你唔洗落樓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"夠25 未甩呢？"},{"pid":"0e68be147fc8cfb78898f6f740bf58713883eb92","tid":2066510,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57afebd4ef9aea474ba58d611ddd59e17d734a0b","tid":2066510,"uid":57186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf107da9a9bec88de29fa24d9fc10218a4ce427f","tid":2066510,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0